amp]] & [[Taylor Gang Entertainment#Raven Felix|Raven Felix]])\n\n===2016===\n\n'''[[Shy Glizzy]] - Young Jefe 2'''\n* 04. \"New Crack\"<ref>{{cite web|title=Shy Glizzy - Young Jefe 2 |url=https://www.discogs.com/Shy-Glizzy-Young-Jefe-2/release/8859378|website=Discogs.com|accessdate=December 27, 2018}}</ref>\n\n'''Tha Joker & Doughboy Beatz - October 31: The Mixtape'''<ref>{{cite web|title=TIDAL: Listen to October 31st on TIDAL|url=https://tidal.com/browse/album/67547255|website=Discogs.com|accessdate=December 27, 2018}}</ref>\n* 01. \"Old Ways\"\n* 02. \"Bandit\"\n* 03. \"Soir\u00e9e\"\n* 05. \"Juice\"\n* 07. \"Run Up\"\n* 08. \"4 A.M.\"\n\n===2017===\n\n'''Doe Boy - In FreeBandz We Trust 2'''\n* 01. \"Savage Back\"\n\n'''Money Man - Secret Society'''\n* 01. \"Secret Society\" <small>(Produced with Trauma Tone)</small>\n\n'''[[Shy Glizzy]] - Quiet Storm'''\n* 01. \"Quiet Storm\"  \n* 11. \"Keep It Goin\"\n\n'''[[Starlito]] & [[Don Trip]] - Step Brothers 3''' \n* 13. \"Remember\"\n\n'''[[Starlito]] - Manifest Destiny'''\n* 04. \"Too Much\" <small>(Produced with [[Metro Boomin]])</small>\n\n'''Tha Joker - Why So Serious 3?'''\n* 01. \"45\" \n* 02. \"Run Up\"  \n* 03. \"Blue Strips\" <small>(Produced with Trauma Tone)</small>\n* 05. \"4 A.M\"  \n* 09. \"Piece Of Mind\"  \n* 10. \"I'd Rather\"\n\n===2018===\n\n'''[[Gunna (rapper)|Gunna]] - [[Drip Season 3]]'''\n* 05. \"Pedestrian\" <small>(Produced with [[Metro Boomin]] & [[Wheezy (record producer)|Wheezy]])</small><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.xxlmag.com/news/2018/03/rich-the-kid-the-world-is-yours-album-production-credits/|title=Stream Gunna's 'Drip Season 3' Mixtape|publisher=[[XXL (magazine)|XXL]]|accessdate=December 26, 2018}}</ref>\n\n'''[[Juicy J]] - 901 Drip''' \n* 11. \"Built\" (feat. YKOM) <small>(Produced with [[Juicy J]] & YK808)</small>\n\n'''Money Man - Grow God''' \n* 09. \"Fake Friends\" <small>(Produced with Trauma Tone)</small>\n\n'''[[NBA Youngboy]] - [[4Respect 4Freedom 4Loyalty 4WhatImportant]]'''